Also, take a look at glpi.sh to understand NUYVM's GLPI automation 

#######################################################################################

This script assumes that you already have sudo configured for the user wich executes it

Please, download glpi.sh to your machine and make it executable 
Do sh glpi.sh 

Login to your GLPI server by your browser with user glpi and password glpi
Don't forget to change this password! 


